import React, { Component } from "react"; import Box from "../Box/Box"; import "./Grid.css"; class Grid extends Component { constructor(props) { super(props); } addRow(){ for(var row = 0; row < 10; row++){ var ele = document.createElement('tr'); ele.id = row; for(var col = 0; col < 10; col++){ var temp = document.createElement('td'); temp.innerHTML = ""; temp.id = "" + row + "-" + col; ele.appendChild(temp); } document.getElementById("grid").firstChild.appendChild(ele); } } render() { return (
); } PrintEle(ele) { console.log(ele); } } export default Grid;
